---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
const updated = "2 June 2026";
---

<BaseLayout
  title="Privacy Policy — Australian Tax Calculator"
  description="Privacy policy for the Australian Tax Calculator. Learn what data we collect, how it is used, and your rights."
>
  <Fragment slot="head">
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="/styles.css" />
  </Fragment>

  <main class="container">

    <section class="card">
      <h2>Privacy Policy</h2>
      <p class="meta">Last updated: {updated}</p>
      <p>
        This Privacy Policy explains how the Australian Tax Calculator ("we", "us", "our") handles
        information when you use this website. We are committed to protecting your privacy and
        being transparent about our practices.
      </p>
    </section>

    <section class="card">
      <h3>1. Information We Collect</h3>

      <h4>Information you enter into the calculator</h4>
      <p>
        Salary figures, selected tax year, and calculator options (resident status, HELP debt,
        super inclusion) are processed entirely in your browser. This data is <strong>never
        transmitted to our servers</strong>. It is stored locally in your browser's local storage
        solely to display your calculation history — it remains on your device and is cleared when
        you click "Clear History" or clear your browser data.
      </p>

      <h4>Automatically collected information</h4>
      <p>
        Like most websites, our hosting provider may collect standard server log data including your
        IP address, browser type, operating system, referring URL, and pages visited. This
        information is used for security monitoring and aggregate traffic analysis only. We do not
        use this data to identify individual users.
      </p>

      <h4>Cookies</h4>
      <p>
        We use cookies from the following third-party services:
      </p>
      <ul>
        <li>
          <strong>Google AdSense</strong> — serves advertisements on this site. Google may use
          cookies to personalise ads based on your browsing history. You can manage ad
          personalisation at <a href="https://adssettings.google.com" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">adssettings.google.com</a>.
        </li>
        <li>
          <strong>Analytics (if applicable)</strong> — aggregate, anonymised usage statistics to
          help us understand which pages are most useful. No personally identifiable information
          is collected.
        </li>
      </ul>
    </section>

    <section class="card">
      <h3>2. How We Use Information</h3>
      <p>We use the information collected to:</p>
      <ul>
        <li>Operate and improve the calculator and website</li>
        <li>Monitor for abuse, security incidents, and technical errors</li>
        <li>Display relevant advertisements through Google AdSense</li>
        <li>Understand aggregate usage patterns to improve content</li>
      </ul>
      <p>We do <strong>not</strong>:</p>
      <ul>
        <li>Sell or share personal data with third parties for marketing</li>
        <li>Store your salary or financial inputs on our servers</li>
        <li>Use your data to build individual profiles</li>
        <li>Send marketing emails (we collect no email addresses)</li>
      </ul>
    </section>

    <section class="card">
      <h3>3. Third-Party Services</h3>
      <p>
        This site uses Google AdSense to display advertising. Google's use of cookies enables it
        to serve ads based on your visits to this and other websites. Google's privacy policy is
        available at <a href="https://policies.google.com/privacy" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">policies.google.com/privacy</a>.
      </p>
      <p>
        We are not responsible for the privacy practices of third-party sites linked from our
        content. We encourage you to review the privacy policies of any site you visit.
      </p>
    </section>

    <section class="card">
      <h3>4. Data Retention</h3>
      <p>
        Calculation history is stored only in your own browser's local storage. You can delete
        it at any time by clicking "Clear History" in the calculator or by clearing your browser's
        site data. Server log data retained by our hosting provider is subject to their own
        retention policies (typically 30–90 days).
      </p>
    </section>

    <section class="card">
      <h3>5. Your Rights</h3>
      <p>
        Because we do not collect or store personally identifiable information about you, most
        formal data subject rights (access, correction, deletion) are not applicable in practice.
        However, if you have any privacy-related concerns or questions, please contact us via the
        <a href="/contact/">Contact page</a>.
      </p>
    </section>

    <section class="card">
      <h3>6. Changes to This Policy</h3>
      <p>
        We may update this Privacy Policy from time to time. The "Last updated" date at the top
        of this page reflects the most recent revision. Continued use of the site following any
        changes constitutes your acceptance of the updated policy.
      </p>
    </section>

    <div class="back-link">
      <a href="/">&larr; Back to the calculator</a>
    </div>

  </main>
</BaseLayout>

<style>
  main {
    padding-top: 2rem;
    padding-bottom: 3rem;
  }

  .card {
    background: #fff;
    border-radius: var(--radius, 12px);
    padding: 1.75rem 2rem;
    box-shadow: var(--shadow, 0 2px 12px rgba(0,0,0,0.08));
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 0.875rem;
  }

  h2 {
    font-size: 1.6rem;
    font-weight: 700;
    color: var(--au-navy, #00205b);
  }

  h3 {
    font-size: 1.1rem;
    font-weight: 700;
    color: var(--au-navy, #00205b);
    border-left: 4px solid var(--au-gold, #ffcd00);
    padding-left: 0.75rem;
  }

  h4 {
    font-weight: 600;
    color: #374151;
    font-size: 0.95rem;
  }

  p, li {
    color: #374151;
    line-height: 1.7;
    font-size: 0.95rem;
  }

  ul {
    padding-left: 1.5rem;
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 0.35rem;
  }

  a {
    color: var(--au-navy, #00205b);
    font-weight: 500;
  }

  .meta {
    color: #64748b;
    font-size: 0.85rem;
  }

  .back-link {
    padding: 0.5rem 0 1rem;
  }

  .back-link a {
    font-size: 0.95rem;
    text-decoration: none;
  }

  .back-link a:hover {
    text-decoration: underline;
  }

  @media (max-width: 640px) {
    .card { padding: 1.25rem 1rem; }
  }
</style>
